// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0580 — Mass File Rename (dispossessor)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a968bc97-7687-5614-b311-7367bc89a825

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
